百度等国产输入法（ Gboard 的中文词库真的太少了）\r\n\r\n- Gboard→国产输入法：直接点小地球即可，很方便\r\n- 国产输入法→Gboard：小地球没了，必须得进系统设置里面更改输入法，非常繁琐，这是问题所在。\r\n\r\n想寻找一款支持快速切换到 Gboard 的中文输入法，各位有没有什么推荐呢？", "content_rendered": "<p>我输入日语和泰语时用 Gboard （日语泰语词库全，语言识别准确）\n我输入中文用搜狗/讯飞/百度等国产输入法（ Gboard 的中文词库真的太少了）</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Gboard→国产输入法：直接点小地球即可，很方便</li>\n<li>国产输入法→Gboard：小地球没了，必须得进系统设置里面更改输入法，非常繁琐，这是问题所在。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>想寻找一款支持快速切换到 Gboard 的中文输入法，各位有没有什么推荐呢？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1707652507, "replies": 20, "id": 1015349}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/22fb/0cee/870_large.png?m=1645249277", "name": "earphone", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/22fb/0cee/870_normal.png?m=1645249277", "title": "耳机", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/earphone", "topics": 404, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Earphone", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/22fb/0cee/870_mini.png?m=1645249277", "stars": 162, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 870, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 625525, "username": "zhousir5071", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/zhousir5071", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a76c/3636/625525_mini.png?m=1707103954", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a76c/3636/625525_normal.png?m=1707103954", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a76c/3636/625525_large.png?m=1707103954", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a76c/3636/625525_xlarge.png?m=1707103954", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a76c/3636/625525_xlarge.png?m=1707103954", "created": 1682234315, "last_modified": 1707103954}, "last_reply_by": "SiuRayyy", "last_touched": 1707693911, "title": "求推荐性价比高，体验好的降噪耳机", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1015338", "created": 1707644979, "deleted": 0, "content": "目前手上有一个 airpods 2 代。想入手一个降噪耳机，我知道 airpods pro2 很香，但实在觉得 airpods pro2 有点太贵了，1500-1800 呢。\r\n\r\n前段时间买了漫步者 W820NB 双金标，降噪还不错，音质也还可以，价格才 238 。唯一就是觉得头戴式的太重，有点夹头，而且在公司使用有点太张扬了。\r\n\r\n我的诉求是：降噪排第一，音质别太差，佩戴要舒适，适合长期佩戴，也不能导致中耳炎。（可以理解为漫步者 w820nb 双金标的入耳式平替版）\r\n\r\n目前有几个考虑：\r\noppo enco free3\r\nvivo tws3\r\n红米 buds4 pro\r\noppo enco x2 （看报道说这款容易导致中耳炎）\r\n\r\n想听听各位大佬们的意见", "content_rendered": "目前手上有一个 airpods 2 代。想入手一个降噪耳机，我知道 airpods pro2 很香，但实在觉得 airpods pro2 有点太贵了，1500-1800 呢。<br /><br />前段时间买了漫步者 W820NB 双金标，降噪还不错，音质也还可以，价格才 238 。唯一就是觉得头戴式的太重，有点夹头，而且在公司使用有点太张扬了。<br /><br />我的诉求是：降噪排第一，音质别太差，佩戴要舒适，适合长期佩戴，也不能导致中耳炎。（可以理解为漫步者 w820nb 双金标的入耳式平替版）<br /><br />目前有几个考虑：<br />oppo enco free3<br />vivo tws3<br />红米 buds4 pro<br />oppo enco x2 （看报道说这款容易导致中耳炎）<br /><br />想听听各位大佬们的意见", "last_modified": 1707647579, "replies": 18, "id": 1015338}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1700771269", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1700771269", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 61308, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1700771269", "stars": 8846, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 539019, "username": "ChrisFreeMan", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ChrisFreeMan", "website": "http://www.simark.link", "twitter": "ChrisWantBeFree", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "love NeoVim, love JavaScript ecosystem, love python language, love freedom. hate Xcode.\r\n\r\n\r\n我的作品： http://www.simark.link\r\n\r\n所见即所得markdown编辑器。", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f6c2/fb66/539019_mini.png?m=1705311623", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f6c2/fb66/539019_normal.png?m=1705311623", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f6c2/fb66/539019_large.png?m=1705311623", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f6c2/fb66/539019_xlarge.png?m=1705311623", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f6c2/fb66/539019_xlarge.png?m=1705311623", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f6c2/fb66/539019_xlarge.png?m=1705311623", "created": 1616471485, "last_modified": 1705311623}, "last_reply_by": "vituralfuture", "last_touched": 1706841086, "title": "为什么对一个语言熟悉以后就很想换个语言重新试一试。", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1015368", "created": 1707663822, "deleted": 0, "content": "我写 TypeScript 已经差两个月一年了,写了有 3 万多行的 TS 代码，老实说还远没有精通这个语言，只是熟悉。能够用来完成想做的项目，但是却一直爱不上这个语言，总是在找其他语言更好的替代方案，比如说 python 。虽然 js 的生态可以做几乎任何我想做的事情，而且专业，但是我还是更喜欢我的初恋语言 python ，奈何 python 能做的事情并没有 js 那么多，比如说桌面和移动端开发领域，以及前端领域。js 生态是真的把我绑死了。如何打消这种换语言的念头。", "content_rendered": "<p>我写 TypeScript 已经差两个月一年了,写了有 3 万多行的 TS 代码，老实说还远没有精通这个语言，只是熟悉。能够用来完成想做的项目，但是却一直爱不上这个语言，总是在找其他语言更好的替代方案，比如说 python 。虽然 js 的生态可以做几乎任何我想做的事情，而且专业，但是我还是更喜欢我的初恋语言 python ，奈何 python 能做的事情并没有 js 那么多，比如说桌面和移动端开发领域，以及前端领域。js 生态是真的把我绑死了。如何打消这种换语言的念头。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1707663822, "replies": 18, "id": 1015368}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 215115, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4088, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 668332, "username": "lx01xsz", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/lx01xsz", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d59f5aec088555934835030f6bfb733f?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d59f5aec088555934835030f6bfb733f?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravat